Mix together yogurt, cucumber, garlic, lemon juice, salt, and pepper in medium bowl. Chill, covered, 1 hour. Brush both sides of pitas lightly with oil. Heat in batches in large skillet over medium heat, 3 to 4 minutes per side, until golden and puffed. Serve pitas with tzatziki and souvlaki (Recipe name: Pork Souvlaki).